            <p>
               <g type="cross">+</g>
               <lb/> Εἷς θ<unclear>ε</unclear>ὀ<unclear>ς</unclear>, ὁ <choice>
                  <orig>π<unclear>ό</unclear>ν<lb break="no"/>των</orig>
                  <reg>πάντων</reg>
               </choice> Δεσπ<unclear>ὀ</unclear>της. <choice>
                  <orig>Μ<lb break="no"/>νημῖον</orig>
                  <reg>Μνημεῖον</reg>
               </choice>
               <supplied reason="lost">Μ</supplied>
               <unclear>ολέχ</unclear>η <choice>
                  <orig>Π<lb break="no"/>λου</orig>
                  <reg>Παύλου</reg>
               </choice>, ἀπ<supplied reason="lost">οθα</supplied>νούσης<lb/> μετά καλοῦ
                  <unclear>ὀ</unclear>νόμ<lb break="no"/>ατ<unclear>ο</unclear>ς καὶ καλῆς <supplied reason="omitted">πίστεως</supplied>ἐν ἔτους<lb/>
               <choice>
                  <orig>τριακοσσιοστοῦ</orig>
